<div class="row">
<div class ="intro">
  <!--h1>📥 Send foods 🍆 </h1-->
  <div class="giant">🍆 🍑 👅</div>
  <h3 ><span class="header-text">Find out what folks are eating</span></h3>
  <p>
    Slide into the feeds of millions of daily Venmo users all across the globe.
    Each minute, the SendFoods Emojilytics™ engine crunches data on the emoji people are
    using to describe their payments and requests. Find out what people are
    sending each other money for.
  </p>
  <h5><span class="header-text">Hey trends...U up? 😏 </span></h5>
  <p>
    The SendFoods Big Board shows near-realtime sampling of the venmo transactions that have happened
    over the past hour. Check out the trending column to see if for recent upticks
     of emoji usages. Click through an emoji to see how it stacks up against other
     popular emoji.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="top-ten-list">
<h3> Top Venmo Transactions <br>(Past Hour)</h3>
<table class="table table-striped">
  <tr>
  <th scope="col">Rank</th>
  <th scope="col">Emoji</th>
  </tr>

  <% @hourly_list.each_with_index do |emoji, i| %>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <%= i + 1 %>
      </td>
      <td>
        <%= link_to emoji[0], {:controller => "messages", :action => "show", :emoji => emoji[0]}, class: "listed-emoji"  %>
      </td>

    </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
</div>
</div>
</div>
